as using them to do the most calculated math problem, and that math problem was me.', 6842, 0), (353994, 'When he flashed that rockin’ smile of his again, I couldn’t help but think that me being cute was what might be crossing his mind. Then again, maybe he thought I was a dumbass. Either way, he smiled, which was good enough for me. - Ariel', 41023, 0), (353995, 'He gazed deeply into my eyes. Placing his hand to my cheek, he caressed my skin with his fingertips. “Ariel, you have a strength that cannot be hindered by anything. A strength that I admire greatly.” - Luca', 41023, 0), (353996, 'And if I ever see you or your fake ass Chanel earrings around here again, I will shove my very real, very pointy Jimmy Choos up your prissy little ass. Do I make myself clear?', 6842, 0), (353997, 'That girl was a goddess and once a guy got hooked on her it was damn hard weaning off. - Drake', 41023, 0), (353998, 'I became insane, with long intervals of horrible sanity.', 49, 0), (353999, 'I''ll take crazy over stupid any day.', 1099, 0), (354000, 'The Edge... There is no honest way to explain it because the only people who really know where it is are the ones who have gone over.', 126, 0);
